command ./lens -config ./configs/test


main=================  the main body
def.h
display_opengl.h=====  basic opengl drawing
file_parse.h=========  read the configuration file
geometry.h  =========  ray geometry
image_view.h=========  image window
lens_view.h =========  lens window
lens_model.h=========  thick lens model including lens intrinsic calculation
					   draw intrinsic properties
microlens_model.h====  microlens model
ray_trace.h =========  trace ray for lens window and image window
transform.cpp========  matrix transfomration

==========================================================================
GUI KEY BOARD MAP

ESC: quit

*****Lens Window*****
b  : background
s  : save
,  : stop +
.  : stop -
o  : image plane + 0.1
p  : image plane - 0.1
k  : image plane + 0.02
l  : image plane - 0.02
u  : object plane + 5
i  : object plane - 5 
h  : object plane + 0.5
j  : object plane - 0.5
t  : microlens array plane - 0.1
y  : microlens array plane + 0.1 

*****Image Window*****
b  : background
m  : mode
z  : save
=  : zoom out
-  : zomm in
a  : image move left
s  : image move right
d  : image move up
f  : image move down
o  : image plane + 0.1
p  : image plane - 0.1 
k  : image plane + 0.02
l  : image plane - 0.02




